      • getPropertyTypeByName

        public PropertyType getPropertyTypeByName(java.lang.String name)
        This method (creates and) gives PropertyType-Objects. The new propertytype will be registered in the project. The implementation is alike the singleton-pattern. The method will save the updated list of property types to the database.
        Parameters:
        name - - the name of the property type, that will be created, if it does not already exist
        Returns:
        the property type that was created or found in the dynamic properties list
